Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:26.05,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\frz13.829\pos(867,67)}不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:28.68,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這顆滿載夢想的心靈
